data.description: Escape to your own private retreat in the idyllic rural countryside of East Tennessee with this charming 5 bedroom, 2 bath home. Spread across two stories, this spacious home offers plenty of room for your family and guests. Enjoy easy access to the lake perfect for those lazy summer days spent swimming, fishing, or simply soaking up the sun. The sunroom is the perfect spot to relax and take in the serene views of the countryside. The detached garage features a 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom apartment, providing extra living space or potential rental income. This home has endless potential and provides the perfect opportunity to add your own personal touch and make it your own. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to live in a spacious home with lake access in the peaceful countryside of East Tennessee!
